Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.56,0:01:56.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等我啊 老板
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.63,0:01:57.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快点过来
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.56,0:01:59.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.09,0:02:04.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在干嘛呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.23,0:02:05.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.92,0:02:10.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好棒的景色
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.66,0:02:13.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,二楼以上主要是住宿设施
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.68,0:02:19.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最上层的大厅是给赌场的客人休息高级酒吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.44,0:02:23.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是这样的城堡不是一般都会有着可怕的幽灵传说吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.21,0:02:26.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.99,0:02:31.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别介意 有一两只幽灵反而会是个卖点
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.50,0:02:33.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃 真有这种传说吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.94,0:02:34.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁知道呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.93,0:02:36.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来 接下来是地下室
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.03,0:02:38.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,地下室…？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.50,0:02:39.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老板
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.71,0:02:46.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,19世纪 最后的城主米萨莉
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.85,0:02:50.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,据说在这个城堡里经营着赌场
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.56,0:02:52.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她就是米萨莉
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.27,0:02:59.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好漂亮的人儿
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.97,0:03:02.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错 是个好女人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.98,0:03:07.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这次霍华德度假村把这城堡移植到了这个岛上
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.26,0:03:10.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,忠实地重现了当时的赌场
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.70,0:03:14.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过嘛 桌子和霍华德度假村用的是同一个型号的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.19,0:03:15.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,修缮费用也不多
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.19,0:03:17.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厉害…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.89,0:03:18.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.93,0:03:23.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了把当时的气氛毫无损失地呈现给客人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.46,0:03:25.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就换上我为你准备的服装吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.08,0:03:29.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个充满古城风味的赌场
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.33,0:03:32.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如何 你不觉得是最叫好的卖点嘛？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.65,0:03:34.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过幽灵还是免了吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.95,0:03:37.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等到改建工作完成 下周就会开业
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.03,0:03:39.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我很指望你哦 莉欧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.76,0:03:43.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是啊老板 我不能在酒店的赌场之上还兼做这里啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.76,0:03:46.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算现在 要干你交给我的各种事情 都已经完全没有休息了…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.84,0:03:50.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放心吧 我已经准备了一个新的Dealer
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.61,0:03:53.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又有新人…？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.70,0:03:55.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 这次的可是有经验的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.65,0:03:59.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之 不许失败
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.72,0:04:02.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可是在这个城堡上花了一大笔钱的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.78,0:04:04.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不成功的话就损失大了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.71,0:04:06.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是～
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.42,0:04:27.95,title_op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an5\pos(846,615)}MISERY
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.37,0:04:54.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晚…晚上好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.84,0:05:02.84,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a5}注：此处赌的是21点，即两张牌之和最接近二十一点的人获胜
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.01,0:05:06.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,20 庄家是18
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.85,0:05:08.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恭喜你
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.07,0:05:12.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来决胜吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.55,0:05:18.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是我赢了 这座赌场我就收下了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.48,0:05:20.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,客人您太会开玩笑了…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.38,0:05:42.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来是梦啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.12,0:05:59.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讨厌 最讨厌打雷了！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.77,0:06:24.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小莉欧 就是那个笑容！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.09,0:06:26.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀 你还真是闪亮动人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.20,0:06:28.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光彩夺目啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.03,0:06:42.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,OK  辛苦了 小莉欧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.23,0:06:44.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常感谢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.29,0:06:53.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给 莉欧 辛苦啦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.84,0:06:54.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.27,0:07:03.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人气真高啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.81,0:07:05.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,罗纱小姐！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.27,0:07:10.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样连好莱坞也会来挖墙脚的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.01,0:07:12.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敏特好想看莉欧演的电影～
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.20,0:07:14.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巧可也是这样想的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.86,0:07:15.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讨厌
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.91,0:07:18.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨天雷打得好厉害啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.38,0:07:22.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗 我睡得很死都没注意
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.73,0:07:26.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莉欧！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.28,0:07:29.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾露 伊露
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.06,0:07:34.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听说了吗 昨天的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.09,0:07:36.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事情
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.41,0:07:37.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发生什么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.62,0:07:38.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鸡翅啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.40,0:07:39.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,翅啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.23,0:07:43.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听说昨晚度假村内餐饮店里的鸡翅膀 一个晚上就全不见了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.93,0:07:44.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不见了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.88,0:07:45.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鸡翅膀？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.87,0:07:46.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 是我
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.97,0:07:49.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思 能帮我把餐馆的预约取消了不
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.35,0:07:50.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错 麻烦你了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.08,0:07:54.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不吃东西也变胖了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.83,0:07:56.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在节食？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.00,0:07:58.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上起来吓了我一跳
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.72,0:08:00.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无所谓 反正我也没什么食欲
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.92,0:08:02.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做演员也不容易啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.02,0:08:05.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是演员 是好莱坞女星哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.67,0:08:16.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Have a lucky day～
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.17,0:08:29.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,中了！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.35,0:08:35.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.63,0:08:36.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,故障了？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.22,0:08:42.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来今天手气不行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.53,0:08:44.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也该回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.65,0:08:57.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起 对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.32,0:09:01.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.20,0:09:04.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无所谓了 反正手气也不好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.53,0:09:05.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,客人！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.30,0:09:10.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常抱歉 非常抱歉！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.80,0:09:16.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那啥…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.41,0:09:27.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来决胜吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.70,0:09:36.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是我赢了 这座赌场我就收下了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.56,0:09:37.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的 客人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.78,0:09:39.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.38,0:09:47.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起 对不起！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.92,0:09:55.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小球…小球…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.98,0:09:58.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,客人 实在非常抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.50,0:10:01.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您想喝点那边的什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.09,0:10:01.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用了！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.94,0:10:02.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找到了！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.13,0:10:13.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,客人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.44,0:10:38.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,赢了就收下赌场…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.84,0:10:40.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她是这么说的吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.49,0:10:41.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的 莉欧前辈
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.68,0:10:46.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 真是不知廉耻的女人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.94,0:10:48.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她长什么样子？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.39,0:10:49.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以前没见过的客人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.32,0:10:51.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,穿着红色的晚装
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.01,0:10:53.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,红色的晚装？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.36,0:10:55.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然是很漂亮 但是总觉得很阴沉
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.55,0:10:58.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟我的梦一样
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.09,0:10:59.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梦？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.80,0:11:02.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶！看这个！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.60,0:11:09.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样看不清脸啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.63,0:11:10.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看不清
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.87,0:11:13.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然是超自然现象…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.41,0:11:14.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别说傻话
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.45,0:11:16.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肯定是用了些干扰电磁波之类的装置
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.00,0:11:18.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,停电肯定也是因为这个
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.52,0:11:23.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蒂芙妮 要是下次这个女人再出现 马上叫警卫
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.96,0:11:24.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.57,0:11:27.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿妮娅
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.39,0:11:28.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.21,0:11:29.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟我一起来
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.42,0:11:36.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莉 莉欧前辈我好怕…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.41,0:11:38.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没 没事的 抓紧我的手
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.11,0:11:41.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么要把灯光搞得这么昏暗啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.78,0:11:43.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老板的喜好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.09,0:11:45.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对对 就是她
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.12,0:11:47.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再好好看看
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.97,0:11:50.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千真万确 就是这个人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.54,0:11:52.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么说…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.40,0:11:54.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她是谁？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.62,0:11:57.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,米萨莉的幽灵…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.31,0:11:58.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幽灵？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.30,0:12:22.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是啥？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.20,0:12:22.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啥？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.22,0:12:28.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听到了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.20,0:12:28.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.41,0:13:14.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们看到了吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.20,0:13:19.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说幽灵？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.66,0:13:22.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错 是米萨莉的幽灵
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.43,0:13:24.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿妮娅也通过她的画像确认了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.95,0:13:27.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老——板！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.02,0:13:31.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在给城堡付款的时候 我也听说过有幽灵
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.80,0:13:33.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看坦白了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.43,0:13:39.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那又如何？幽灵啥的是不可能存在的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.58,0:13:41.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.65,0:13:44.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在网上搜了些关于米萨莉的资料
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.81,0:13:45.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说你啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.23,0:13:49.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,米萨莉深深地沉迷于赌博中
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.38,0:13:54.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她在城堡里开的赌场 也因为她是美女城主而闻名
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.59,0:13:55.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.33,0:14:01.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她当时和一个有钱的大赌棍对战了一局花旗骰
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.33,0:14:01.04,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a5}花旗骰（Craps）：用两粒骰子来进行的赌博游戏。\N此处对手赌棍投出7点，按规则为赢家
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.80,0:14:07.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一夜间所有的财产都输光了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.67,0:14:10.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从城堡的所有权 到鸡翅膀
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.35,0:14:12.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鸡翅膀？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.77,0:14:14.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鸡翅膀是米萨莉最喜欢吃的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.27,0:14:17.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这和度假村内的鸡翅膀消失事件吻合
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.45,0:14:19.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一派胡言
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.62,0:14:23.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,米萨莉死后 虽然城堡交由他人之手继续经营
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.96,0:14:28.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是因为在城内经常会目击到米萨莉的幽灵
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.61,0:14:32.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,赌场经营情况急转直下 最后倒闭了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.76,0:14:33.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,狗屁不通！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.62,0:14:34.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老板！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.87,0:14:37.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都有这么多的证据了 你还不做点什么吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.16,0:14:39.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么破证据
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.58,0:14:42.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那好 退一万步说有幽灵存在
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.94,0:14:47.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 没有肉体的幽灵为什么能吃鸡翅呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.86,0:14:48.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是因为…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.30,0:14:50.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.76,0:14:53.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…为什么呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.64,0:15:23.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.82,0:15:31.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 石头脑袋
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.43,0:15:35.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,罗纱小姐？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.30,0:15:37.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好 我是莉欧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.90,0:15:41.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.08,0:15:47.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快…快点…救我…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.35,0:15:48.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,罗纱小姐？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.78,0:15:51.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在我…丧失自我之前…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.33,0:15:52.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,罗纱小姐 罗纱小姐！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.16,0:16:06.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不吃东西也变胖了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.51,0:16:10.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,米萨莉在罗纱小姐体内…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.19,0:16:27.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,罗纱小姐？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.28,0:16:34.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是演员罗纱·卡农小姐吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.53,0:16:37.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是你的粉丝 请跟我握手吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.09,0:16:47.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,罗纱小姐！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.06,0:16:58.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,罗纱小姐！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.39,0:17:09.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欢迎来到我的城堡 莉欧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.90,0:17:13.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你…你是米萨莉
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.72,0:17:16.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把罗纱小姐的身体还给她！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.64,0:17:19.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没问题啊 但是作为交换…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.79,0:17:24.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来决胜吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.79,0:17:27.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你赢了的话我把罗纱还给你
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.26,0:17:28.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是你输了的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.11,0:17:29.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,输了的话？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.99,0:17:33.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,霍华德度假村就由我收下了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.65,0:17:34.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绝不允许！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.58,0:17:37.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我绝对不承认这个赌局！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.04,0:17:38.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老板！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.30,0:17:40.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾露 伊露？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.34,0:17:44.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这两人把我硬塞到这里面了！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.22,0:17:55.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是拒绝的话这人的身体就要一分为二了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.14,0:17:57.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快点接受赌局吧莉欧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.09,0:18:00.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没问题吧 賭上度假村
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.35,0:18:01.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.22,0:18:02.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是老板…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.86,0:18:05.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明白啦 允许！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.69,0:18:06.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我上了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.76,0:18:07.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是等等！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.91,0:18:08.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你到底要怎样
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.92,0:18:10.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老子也不知道啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.24,0:18:16.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是我赢了 你真的会释放罗纱小姐吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.56,0:18:17.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.48,0:18:20.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要老老实实回去你的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.89,0:18:22.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我答应你
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.71,0:18:23.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来 决胜吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.14,0:18:26.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,悉从客人所愿
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.07,0:18:38.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们来玩简单的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.91,0:18:42.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,赌两个骰子之和是奇数还是偶数
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.20,0:18:43.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.30,0:18:45.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你来掷骰子吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.77,0:18:46.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,OK
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.99,0:18:54.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快点掷骰子吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.54,0:18:56.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你赌哪个
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.89,0:18:57.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奇数
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.76,0:18:59.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别输啊 莉欧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.36,0:19:02.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,霍华德度假村是我的命根啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.11,0:19:03.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绝对要赢 这是命令！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.66,0:19:19.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她在干啥呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.22,0:19:22.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了？快点掷啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.51,0:19:23.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怕输吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.05,0:19:27.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋 住手啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.29,0:19:29.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来 快点
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.29,0:19:32.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是不行！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.34,0:19:43.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 好辣！这鸡翅搞啥啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.99,0:19:45.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就应该是辣的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.11,0:19:46.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.07,0:19:51.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可是在那鸡翅里面塞满了哈巴内罗辣椒哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.07,0:19:51.34,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a5}哈巴内罗辣椒（Habanero chili）\N原产古巴，据说是世界上最辣的辣椒之一
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.57,0:19:56.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,消失了！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.69,0:20:06.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来 把罗纱小姐还来！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.23,0:20:19.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,罗纱小姐！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.54,0:20:25.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快点停下来！停下来啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.01,0:20:35.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,得救了…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.69,0:20:38.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事吧 罗纱小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.62,0:20:44.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没啥 我只是对被幽灵附体的感觉有兴趣罢了…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.71,0:20:47.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不愧是好莱坞女星
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.95,0:20:50.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你该去问她有没事
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.75,0:21:02.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂！快点把我放出去！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.75,0:21:04.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是老板命令！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.30,0:21:06.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话说 那女孩呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.41,0:21:25.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才真是多谢了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.65,0:21:29.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多亏你的机敏救了我们 不过…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.99,0:21:32.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只是不小心预见了事情的发展而已
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.89,0:21:34.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或许是Dealer的直觉吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.12,0:21:35.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Dealer？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.18,0:21:38.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道老板说的新请来的人是…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.96,0:21:41.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好久不见了 莉欧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.97,0:21:44.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,认不出来？是我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.34,0:21:46.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道是…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.69,0:21:47.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莉娜？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.62,0:21:48.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错 莉欧！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.79,0:21:49.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莉娜！
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.99,0:23:28.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莉娜 谢谢你帮了我
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.56,0:23:30.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让我们又像以前那样做好朋友吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.64,0:23:31.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「做好朋友」…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.01,0:23:33.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们都已经不是小孩子啦
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.95,0:23:36.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你还是老样子呢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.93,0:23:39.97,title_ed,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an5\pos(963,645)\be5}SISTERS
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.59,0:23:38.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下集 也交给莉欧吧～
